items.title: Goldman’s Top European IPO Banker Set to Retire After 31 Years
items.description: (Bloomberg) -- Christoph Stanger, one of the longtime leaders in Goldman Sachs Group Inc.’s equity underwriting business across Europe, the Middle East and Africa, is retiring after more than 31 years.
